Workforce development centers in Iowa

workforce_development.Rd

This dataset contains data on workforce development centers in Iowa. Data was scraped by Masoud Nosrati in July 2020 and geocoded by Joel Von Behren in July 2020.

workforce_development

Format

A data frame with 27 rows and 16 variables:

dataset

name of the dataset

classification

type of services offered by datset

id

identification number, not quite row number

counties_served

Counties serviced by the center

type

type of building

street

street address of the center

city

city in which the center is located

state

state in which the center is located

zip

zip code of the center

county

county in which the center is located

phone

phone number of the center

email

email of the center

link

link to center's website

address

search address used in geocoding

longitude

longitude coordinate

latitude

latitude coordinate

Source

https://www.iowaworkforcedevelopment.gov/contact
